I mean, what is this? 1958?

01:05:53.280 --> 01:05:55.874
Give the little wife a blender?

01:05:56.000 --> 01:06:00.516
I mean, it scared me, you know.
In terms of his expectations.

01:06:00.640 --> 01:06:03.438
