around his-- his dad's desk.

01:06:44.680 --> 01:06:47.274
And that you somehow found
his dad's bankbook--

01:06:47.400 --> 01:06:49.914
Oh, no, no. First he said you broke
some mirror in their bathroom.

01:06:50.040 --> 01:06:53.237
And then you found his dad's bankbook
and you somehow threw it in their pool!

01:06:53.360 --> 01:06:56.955
I mean, it's too ridiculous!
The man lies!

01:06:57.080 --> 01:06:59.230
Come in!

01:07:00.960 --> 01:07:02.871
Annie, Bryan's downstairs.

01:07:03.000 --> 01:07:06.072
- I don't want to see him.
- He looks awful.

01:07:06.200 --> 01:07:08.430
Good.

01:07:08.560 --> 01:07:10.869
Excuse me.

01:07:11.000 --> 01:07:13.309
I thought maybe I should help
smooth things over.

01:07:13.440 --> 01:07:15.476
So I took Bryan out for a drink.

01:07:15.600 --> 01:07:19.434
Thought we could
have a talk, man-to-man.

01:07:19.560 --> 01:07:22.393
But as I sat there and listened
to his side of the story...

01:07:22.520 --> 01:07:25.353
